{"tid":25040,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"有無人照過胃鏡？","createTime":"2016-12-06T01:21:24.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-06T03:01:11.000Z","uid":22024,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"332ed39a3ee27628a7c52b8dd2364a965c39c78c","tid":25040,"uid":22024,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-06T01:21:24.000Z","msg":"人愈大個胃好似愈黎愈弱<br />\n胃氣好多<br />\n有時仲多到無胃口食飯<br />\n想照下胃鏡上網搵過資料，價錢好似5k-7k左右<br />\n有無人有經驗？<br />\n邊間好少少？<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f7cb8fa1d823374a18416995e82eb96589612f1c","tid":25040,"uid":39010,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-06T01:25:11.000Z","msg":"醫院照最好 但貴D<br />\n診所都OK 好快搞掂<br />\n但係你咁樣就要照??有無胃痛先?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n腸胃野 個人建議睇下中醫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0834beed011b9893018809672ead0112515d4d06","tid":25040,"uid":22024,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-06T01:30:55.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>醫院照最好 但貴D<br />\n診所都OK 好快搞掂<br />\n但係你咁樣就要照??有無胃痛先?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n腸胃野 個人建議睇下中醫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n其實有時去到食飯時間，例如每日既12點左右<br />\n就會有大量胃氣湧現<br />\n當我吐哂啲胃氣出黎既時候<br />\n就好好肚餓，個胃好似興興地咁<br />\n上網睇過個症狀似乎係胃酸過多<br />\n但係以防估估下，都係想去照照<br />\n<br />\n多謝巴打先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d89e1603ad84db98bd8fbc72d6f87c821377e381","tid":25040,"uid":22024,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-06T02:33:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7055f46f990ac26b5988efc330556352051d3897","tid":25040,"uid":10743,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-06T02:38:48.000Z","msg":"幫推"},{"pid":"c5d9c0c9b7acff6ed4dcf7e265aabf63b4a2941e","tid":25040,"uid":14130,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-06T02:40:41.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"109491e32f049c0d8889d3e649ffa2935e2dbc6a","tid":25040,"uid":38426,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-06T02:42:34.000Z","msg":"係銅鑼灣照過<br />\n關治邦醫生<br />\n大約6k，睇你有冇保險claim<br />\n係東角中心，你Google下<br />\n照完有隻dvd比返你"},{"pid":"946eabfed8c3a13d45a51d65991ea47c30bd5734","tid":25040,"uid":1550,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-06T02:43:34.000Z","msg":"睇左醫生先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2eeec93523f74badcd1a23dd451aded963ddcbb2","tid":25040,"uid":21779,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-06T02:44:30.000Z","msg":"巴打可以試下睇中醫先，如果唔得先睇腸胃科啦，我之前睇私家診所，佢會同你照晒超聲波，吹幽門螺旋桿菌，最後都搞唔掂先照胃鏡，照都係around 4k"},{"pid":"28490f844380e1c15c0855e144a235c8d7b008a2","tid":25040,"uid":22024,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-06T03:01:11.000Z","msg":"多謝咁多位巴打<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n中醫其實睇過<br />\n食左一段時間樂都無咩好轉<br />\n不過先睇西醫將個情況講左俾醫生聽先都岩<br />\n如果佢地覺得我個症狀要照胃鏡先睇得出咁我先去照<br />\n如果就咁食藥物可以改善我個情況仲好<br />\n睇人講照胃鏡既實際情況其實都有少少淆<br />\n無論如何，多謝各位巴打<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}